{"tid":1376490,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"鋼琴自學其實得唔得","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T15:20:52.000Z","uid":167689,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b364198d42108da2216cb2224fc7d73bc8e8d9e","tid":1376490,"uid":167689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"細個考完八級就停咗<br />\n間唔中會上網搵啲易sight read既流行曲自己彈下，但唔會背唔會練熟一首<br />\n早排翻睇完交響情人夢，好想彈古典同練翻琴<br />\n(果時考感覺好兒戲，好似背熟首歌同臨尾彈熟scale就考，好似零基本功咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但出去學好貴，唔知有冇巴絲試過咩途徑自學<br />\n<br />\n些牙其中首劇入面好好聽又似係唔太難既歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mutopiaproject.org/ftp/BeethovenLv/O13/pathetique-2/pathetique-2-a4.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mutopiaproject.org%2Fftp%2FBeethovenLv%2FO13%2Fpathetique-2%2Fpathetique-2-a4.pdf&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=3d07baf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mutopiaproject.org/ftp/BeethovenLv/O13/pathetique-2/pathetique-2-a4.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"751d9b6a024d39315e3eee6487e124e6c4b97cc6","tid":1376490,"uid":79974,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"唔得"},{"pid":"349651386dbad3e4d6db9321b7e410d34a42f123","tid":1376490,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"751d9b6a024d39315e3eee6487e124e6c4b97cc6","tid":1376490,"uid":79974,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:45:37.000Z","msg":"唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:45:58.000Z","msg":"利伸：過來人"},{"pid":"1ca653dca51169864104588306d736f7946f0660","tid":1376490,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:05:27.000Z","msg":"read analyse listen play &lt;- loop loop loop"},{"pid":"93b6d62d9f80a5f5890f143c708c735a1c7f5f78","tid":1376490,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T11:15:24.000Z","msg":"我見過有人自學<br />\n都彈到一首蕭邦nocturne<br />\n不過學壞手勢<br />\n最後都要揾人教<b